      "content": "it's not just being stressed though. it's deeper. i look at them and i just feel this massive amount of guilt. like, if i wasn't in the picture, they wouldn't have to deal with my mistakes or my constant struggle. i feel like a dark cloud hanging over them. wouldn't it be easier for them if they just didn't have to carry me?",
